org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_AnalysisModel.GQAM

Interface GaScenario

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceUsage, TimedElement, TimedProcessing
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GaAcqStep, GaCommStep, GaRelStep, GaRequestedService, GaStep, PaCommStep, PaRequestedStep, PaResPassStep, PaStep, SaCommStep, SaStep
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GaAcqStepImpl, GaCommStepImpl, GaRelStepImpl, GaRequestedServiceImpl, GaScenarioImpl, GaStepImpl, PaCommStepImpl, PaRequestedStepImpl, PaResPassStepImpl, PaStepImpl, SaCommStepImpl, SaStepImpl

    public interface GaScenario
extends ResourceUsage, TimedProcessing
    A representation of the model object 'Ga Scenario'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Cause
    • Host Demand
    • Host Demand Ops
    • Inter Occ T
    • Throughput
    • Resp T
    • Utilization
    • Utilization On Host
    • Root
    • Steps
    • Parent Step
    • Timing
    See Also:
    GQAMPackage.getGaScenario()
